{"tid":2412559,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾醒明被5歲男童踩單車撞倒入院 左額掛彩縫4針膝蓋擦傷流血","createTime":"2021-02-18T06:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T20:36:49.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49e785af013ade665bf1fa557eec06d3625ddfab","tid":2412559,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"有「最強公關」之稱的前無綫企業傳訊部宣傳科副總監曾醒明，年初二返太子給母親拜年後，途經深水埗公園，不幸被一名男童踩單車從身後飛撞，受傷倒地，途人見狀即代叫救護車送院。<br />\n<br />\n曾醒明到醫院檢查後，翌日在FB報平安，並道出事發經過：「一名年約5歲男童，腳踏單車飛馳而至，收掣不及從身後飛撞，在毫無意識驚覺下，整個人被撞倒地，昏了一陣，左眼額頭撞至血流披面，褲子也擦穿，原來左膝蓋也擦傷流血，幸好有途人見義勇為，半攙扶至旁幫忙止血，多張紙巾沾染鮮血，其他人則致電急喚救護車，未幾救傷員到埸作臨時包紮，用擔架送上救傷車，直送明愛醫院。幸好送院前清醒，還懂得安慰驚喊肇事的男童，農曆新年期間的急症室，還好病人不多，經過醫生檢查診治，即埸縫了4針後，安排作電腦掃描，在觀察病房逗留多時，醫生建議留院一晚觀察，擾攘了逾4個小時，後來决定簽字自行回家休息，一星期拆線。」<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210218/YQIAIWRV7ZAEBJN2M5HVOCZQJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210218%2FYQIAIWRV7ZAEBJN2M5HVOCZQJ4%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOuPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=4a93560a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210218%2FYQIAIWRV7ZAEBJN2M5HVOCZQJ4%2F&h=497f40b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210218/YQIAIWRV7ZAEBJN2M5HVOCZQJ4/</a>"},{"pid":"a4e53bd8bfd55f7b996390cdde871bea45824bfb","tid":2412559,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zTv0cYJHZffEt_Sf-vSgIGEQGZE=/339x696/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FQUMWJNDHRF4HKRHFD45KZBTPU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzTv0cYJHZffEt_Sf-vSgIGEQGZE%3D%2F339x696%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFQUMWJNDHRF4HKRHFD45KZBTPU.JPG&h=19f954a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10a7379d206d1073bdfdbb424e39f4afe6a47e18","tid":2412559,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T20:23:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e5351234f3bdc24a90532c6a9d0b304bef57a276","tid":2412559,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T20:36:49.000Z","msg":"我住果度都有細路響籃球場踩單車，撞到個阿婆受傷送醫院。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}